# 1. Purpose

This document defines the strategic roadmap for improving AI governance maturity at SimulFlow.

It translates identified risks, audit gaps, and executive insights into a structured improvement plan.

---

# 2. Strategic Objectives

- Reduce Critical AI risks to zero
- Achieve ISO/IEC 42001 readiness ≥ 95%
- Implement continuous AI monitoring
- Establish formal AI incident response capability
- Mature vendor AI assurance program

---

